blog.name: weirdandwackypokefusions
blog.title: Well that's strange!
blog.description:
Welcome!  I create, using the all-mighty classic Microsoft XP Paint, my own pokemon fusions. All the sprites come from pokestadium and usually people on deviantart/ the xy/sun&moon sprite project. I don't own any of the sprite used, I just fuse them! 
REQUESTS ARE OPEN! Ask Box: 3/15.
PLEASE FEEL FREE TO DRAW MY FUSIONS!!  I absolutely love it when people draw them! There's no need to ask either! Just make sure you tag me so them I can see it!
I hope you enjoy my fusions!

summary:
Pumpkaboo Pie Pumpkaboo and Pumpkin Pie fusion Nutritional Information: Fruit/Bread type Ability: Tin Guard - 

The Pokefood...
caption:
Pumpkaboo Pie

Pumpkaboo and Pumpkin Pie fusion

Nutritional Information:

Fruit/Bread type

Ability: Tin Guard -  The Pokefood only takes damage from attacks.

Signature move - The Pokefood throws its cream on the ground, making the opponent slip on it, causing them to damage themself upon entry.  An entry hazard.  When the opponent switches a pokefood in, it will get damaged by 10% of its hp.

The Pie Pokemon

Pumpkaboo Pie is usually found around kitchens and wishes to help make sweet treats with its trainer.  Its tin can be removed but it doesn’t want that to happen as it’ll feel naked.  

Day 12 and we have a Pumpkaboo and Pumpkin Pie fusion suggested by @irishscottish. I hope you like it. I’ve actually never had pumpkin pie before.
